Breed &amp; Aplin (1995), Dennis &amp; Menzies (1979), Dwyer (1975), Flannery (1995b), Leary, Singadan, Menzies, Wright, Helgen &amp; Aplin (2016a), Musser &amp; Carleton (2005), Smales (2015), Steppan &amp; Schenk (2017).
</subSubSection>
